OL,3,CLaw to be changed to deport grooming
OL,4,Cgang leader
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary is set to change
OL,7,Fthe law to allow the deportation of a
OL,8,FRochdale grooming gang leader who was
OL,9,Freleased from prison last week.
OL,11,FShabana Mahmood is expected to
OL,12,Fannounce plans on Monday, 13 July, to
OL,13,Famend a 1971 law preventing the
OL,14,Fremoval of Shabir Ahmed, 73, from the
OL,15,FUK.
OL,17,FAhmed was released on 2 July after
OL,18,Fserving 14 years for rape and sexual
OL,19,Foffences against girls, some as young
OL,20,Fas 12.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
