OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1783682373
OL,3,CLaw to be changed to deport grooming
OL,4,Cgang leader
OL,6,FKnown to his victims as "Daddy", Ahmed
OL,7,Fhad dual British-Pakistani citizenship
OL,8,Fbut was stripped of his British
OL,9,Fcitizenship following his 2012
OL,10,Fconviction.
OL,12,FIt is not clear whether the changes
OL,13,Fwill come under separate fast-tracked
OL,14,Flegislation or as an amendment to the
OL,15,FImmigration and Asylum Bill, which is
OL,16,Fdue to be debated in the Commons.
OL,18,FA Home Office minister indicated
OL,19,Fearlier this week that the Government
OL,20,Fcould consider emergency legislation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
