CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1783682373
OL,3,CLaw to be changed to deport grooming
OL,4,Cgang leader
OL,6,FAlex Norris said "all options are on
OL,7,Fthe table" as the Conservatives urged
OL,8,Fhim to adopt an amendment to the Bill
OL,9,Fput forward by the shadow home
OL,10,Fsecretary.
OL,12,FAhmed is currently exempt from
OL,13,Fdeportation but Mr Norris said the
OL,14,FGovernment would not give up in its
OL,15,Fefforts to deport Ahmed due to his
OL,16,F"heinous" crimes.
