PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1783682373
OL,3,CLaw to be changed to deport grooming
OL,4,Cgang leader
OL,6,FThe Government has been examining ways
OL,7,Fto deport Ahmed since his release last
OL,8,Fweek. The 1971 law forbids the removal
OL,9,Fof a small group of Commonwealth
OL,10,Fcitizens who arrived in the UK more
OL,11,Fthan 50 years ago.
OL,13,FReports have suggested Pakistan might
OL,14,Fnot accept Ahmed because he had
OL,15,Fpreviously renounced his citizenship,
OL,16,Fbut a Number 10 spokesperson confirmed
OL,17,Fit has raised the issue with officials
OL,18,Fin Islamabad.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
